fillment, CMS, CRM and more.</li></span><span><li>Working knowledge of general principles of open source software, SQL databases, HTML and CSS, web services, and common web technologies integral to building seamless multi-channel experiences.</li></span><span><li>Creative problem solver with ability to adapt quickly in a fast-paced environment and remain positive in the face of a challenge.</li></span><span><li>Experience as a Product Owner in SAFe, Agile, or Scrum methodologies for software development is preferred. Certification is a plus.</li></span><span><li>Experience using JIRA, ADO, Rally or other Issue and Project Tracking software is preferred.<span><br></span><span><br></span></li></span></ul></span></p></div>',
