                    'description' => '<p dir="ltr"><span><strong>WE ARE LOOKING FOR AN EXPERIENCED STORE MANAGER TO JOIN OUR RETAIL TEAM FOR OUR AMAZING STORE IN COPENHAGEN AIRPORT!<span><br></span><span><br></span></strong></span>You will be an ambassador for GANNI. You will work within our beautifully curated stores. The GANNI culture is based on a learning and results-driven mentality. Where everyone is united by a common purpose.<span><br></span><span><br></span>As a GANNI Store Manager, you will lead and inspire your team to always deliver service that is seamless, efficient and dedicated to the client’s needs, and be a true ambassador for the brand both within the store and when out of the store.<span><br></span><span><br></span>You will secure excellent customer experience for every visitor we have in the store, and ensure your team is fully equipped to master the ceremonies of the GANNI universe. You will guide, inspire and bring out the best side of all our GANNI girls, and work with the store team to secure operational excellence of the store to deliver smooth and seamless client experiences -every time.<span><br></span><span><br></span>At GANNI we strive for customized experiences and valued relationships with our clients. Through intelligent clienteling tools, you will drive business, relationships and community to your store, and build your own portfolio of special clients where private stylings require your talent for styling and eagerness to accommodate your clients needs. You’re motivated by achieving targets, both in value and KPIs, and you utilize all the intelligent tools we have available, built around an OMNI channel business model, where missing a sale is never an option. You are confident, while using your talented network of fellow Store Managers across Denmark and Scandinavia. You explore options to achieve your objectives, and use your creativity and proactive mindset, to explore opportunities and new ways to drive retail excellence to the 